<br>
I agree with others that if they are going to make mobs cast spells like that then their HP and combat abilities should be made more in line with their class. I have no problem with them being smart enough to stand back and cast high damage spells, but once they are toe to toe with a warrior they should go down fast, not stand there and fight better than the warrior does.<br>
